Sentencas: Symmetric, free standing thin film micro-solid oxide fuel cells of Pt/Y0.16Zr0.84O1.92/Pt structure are studied in this report.
Titulo: Pt/Y0.16Zr0.84O1.92/Pt thin film solid oxide fuel cells: Electrode microstructure and stability considerations

Sentencas: The role of parameters such as electrolyte thickness and electrode porosity on fuel cell power output was investigated.
Titulo: Pt/Y0.16Zr0.84O1.92/Pt thin film solid oxide fuel cells: Electrode microstructure and stability considerations

Sentencas: A peak power density of 1037 mW cm(-2) was exhibited with an optimized structure consisting of nano-porous Pt electrodes and 100 nm thick Y0.16Zr0.84O1.92 with an open circuit voltage of 0.968 Vat 500 degrees C using H-2 as fuel and standing air as the oxidant.
Titulo: Pt/Y0.16Zr0.84O1.92/Pt thin film solid oxide fuel cells: Electrode microstructure and stability considerations

Sentencas: A twelve hour test of these devices indicates that overall performance shows extreme sensitivity to microstructural changes in the pure metallic electrodes.
Titulo: Pt/Y0.16Zr0.84O1.92/Pt thin film solid oxide fuel cells: Electrode microstructure and stability considerations

Sentencas: Results presented herein enable mechanistic routes to performance optimization, provide device stability data and are relevant to advancing micro-fuel cells for portable energy.
Titulo: Pt/Y0.16Zr0.84O1.92/Pt thin film solid oxide fuel cells: Electrode microstructure and stability considerations
